<p><strong>Medium undead, neutral evil</strong></p>

<p><strong>Armor Class</strong> 14 (studded leather)</p>

<p><strong>Hit Points</strong> 45 (6d8+18)</p>

<p><strong>Speed</strong> 30 ft.</p>

